    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "A five-minute tapping practice from Day 13 of the SLEEP program. The script targets the productivity-equals-worth belief: the internal voice that keeps score, measures days in output, and issues guilt as the penalty for stopping. A daytime practice for loosening that equation."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          { "type": "text", "text": "New to tapping? Read " },
          { "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "link", "attrs": { "href": "/mindset/how-eft-tapping-works" } }], "text": "how EFT tapping works" },
          { "type": "text", "text": " first." }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 2 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "The practice" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Karate chop" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though I feel guilty when I rest, I deeply and completely accept myself." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though I measure my value by how much I do, I honour the culture and conditioning that taught me that." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Even though slowing down feels wrong, I'm open to believing rest is responsible, not selfish." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Tapping round" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I hear the voice that says, \"you should be doing more.\"" }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " That voice pushes me past my limits." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " It confuses busyness with worth." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " It ignores the cost to my body and mind." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I'm allowed to consider another standard." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Collarbone:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " One where rest is part of the job, not a reward." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under arm:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " One where care makes me more effective." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Top of head:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I'm ready to retire guilt as my motivator." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 3 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Reframe to positive" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Eyebrow:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I'm valuable whether I'm working or resting." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Side of eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " Recovery is productive for my nervous system." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under eye:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " Pausing sustains my best self." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under nose:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " Rest protects the life I care about." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Chin:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " My body deserves time to repair." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Collarbone:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I respect my limits without apology." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Under arm:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I choose rest with confidence and self-respect." }] }]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [{ "type": "paragraph", "content": [{ "type": "text", "marks": [{ "type": "bold" }], "text": "Top of head:" }, { "type": "text", "text": " I move through today free from guilt." }] }]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Tap each round three times, then move to the reframe and tap that three times." }]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": { "level": 2 },
        "content": [{ "type": "text", "text": "Where this practice comes from" }]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
