            "type": "text",
            "text": "Adapted from Day 13 of SLEEP: A 30-Day Tapping Intensive to Fall Asleep Faster and Wake Energised (Rebecca J Page, 2025). EFT was developed by Gary Craig in the mid-1990s, building on Roger Callahan's Thought Field Therapy."
